title: Exception throws when exporting data from a table inside a grid cell
description: When exporting data from a table that is inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
OB: When attempting to export data from a table that is inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: When exporting data from two tables, the expected result is that the data are exported successfully. However, the actual result is that an exception occurs in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() function.
SR: To reproduce the issue, follow these steps: 1. Insert a grid. 2. Export data from a table that is inside a grid cell.
